         !text "            Adventure Replay            "
         !text "         GET KEY. UNLOCK STORY.         "
         !text "                                        "
         !text "These are graphical adventure games. You"
         !text "type commands, and the game shows where "
         !text "you are and what's happening there. You "
         !text "can navigate to different locations,    "
         !text "take and use items to solve puzzles, and"
         !text "interact with other characters to move  "
         !text "through the story and win the game.     "
         !text "                                        "
         !text "Most games use two-word commands, like  "
         !text "GET LAMP and LIGHT LAMP. Some games also"
         !text "have limited support for prepositions   "
         !text "(LOOK UNDER BED). It can be challenging "
         !text "to find the right verb/noun combination."
         !text "                                        "
         !text "You usually navigate by typing GO NORTH "
         !text "(or SOUTH or EAST or WEST). Most games  "
         !text "allow you to abbreviate these (N/S/E/W)."
         !text "Most games also support typing AGAIN or "
         !text "pressing up arrow to repeat a command.  "
         !text "                                        "
         !text "LOOK and EXAMINE everything. Good luck! "
         !fill $40
